{"tid":1332882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】召集英國巴絲：聯署爭取將人權條款納入脫歐後同香港嘅自由貿易協議","createTime":"2019-07-19T13:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T21:51:23.000Z","uid":27579,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7cce4cfb2c911d977faf5495059592714dc06f83","tid":1332882,"uid":27579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"大家好，大家都知道本月二十二日左右就會知道保守黨新領袖究竟係約翰遜定係侯俊偉。但無論邊個贏，都會着手處理脫歐問題。一旦脫歐，意味英國政府可能要同唔同國家簽訂新嘅貿易協議。所以我地住係英國嘅巴絲，應該爭取英國仿效美國，將人權議題同貿易掛歐。 <br />\n <br />\n依家有個係英國嘅港人團體發起聯署，希望可以表達我地想英國係脫歐後同香港簽訂嘅自由貿易協議入面，加入人權條款，令英國係處理香港問題上，有更大嘅力量。 <br />\n <br />\n所以麻煩咁多位係英國嘅巴絲將呢個倡議share 出去！等我地嘅聲音被聽見！  <br />\n <br />\n聯署連結： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://you.38degrees.org.uk/petitions/uk-should-safeguard-human-rights-and-rule-of-law-in-hong-kong-in-future-trade-deals?fbclid=IwAR3TPSberyjSaGxnEE3M_WDBlmkqCkv_kRbQJC96df8w2GDs8Y6EARODjtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyou.38degrees.org.uk%2Fpetitions%2Fuk-should-safeguard-human-rights-and-rule-of-law-in-hong-kong-in-future-trade-deals%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3TPSberyjSaGxnEE3M_WDBlmkqCkv_kRbQJC96df8w2GDs8Y6EARODjtY&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=61f28cb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://you.38degrees.org.uk/petitions/uk-should-safeguard-human-rights-and-rule-of-law-in-hong-kong-in-future-trade-deals?fbclid=IwAR3TPSberyjSaGxnEE3M_WDBlmkqCkv_kRbQJC96df8w2GDs8Y6EARODjtY</a>"},{"pid":"4a9acc7d92022752e8ecd24c7c666ad0ffdb126c","tid":1332882,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>保障同行手足</strong></span></span><br />\n【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"865dddd8e1e4074c65e7fbb12a4c6e764e71eb31","tid":1332882,"uid":146583,"like"